  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The sergeant who joined the struggle was arrested with a sharp weapon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police sergeant who supported the struggle in Maharagama town was arrested early this morning (11) while trying to enter the presidential palace with a sharp weapon, said Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Nihal Talduwa.",
        "A sergeant working at Narahenpita Police Garage, a resident of Homagama Magammana area, has been arrested.",
        "A 2 inch wide and 10 inch long manna was found in the possession of the suspect sergeant and taken into police custody.",
        "When the suspect, who was wearing a pair of sandals and wearing a police uniform, came to enter the Presidential Palace, the military officers who were guarding him noticed him and stopped him.",
        "At the same time, a police officer said that after handing over the suspect to the police officers who were guarding him, they took the cell phone of the Fortak police to the place and handed it over to him.",
        "Police say that the arrested police sergeant is the one who supported a group of young people who were marching for struggle in Maharagama town on the last day."
      ],
